data.description: Charming home situated at the end of a cul-de-sac lot.  After some tree damage, home has almost totally been renovated inside. New kitchen has much cabinets with lots of pantry space, new appliances, and flooring.There is no carpet whatsoever.  Large spacious rooms give you flexibility in your uses. Enjoy 15' X15' screened porch, and similar wooden deck overlooking fenced-in backyard. Lot backs up to trees providing privacy and a wooden shed adds storage for your personal items. Property is within a mile of the front gate to Marine Corps Air Station, Cherry Point.  Also, historic New Bern is within 20 miles and the Atlantic Beach is about 30 miles away. This property should sell fast!
